summary: Modders Resource - Adds armor to Skyrim Skeletons
descriptionHtml:
This file comes AS IS.

File contains both .3DS and .OBJ files
Skeletons have been altered slightly to fit the armor.
V1.0 contains 6 Skeletons wearing armor and helmets.
- Iorn
- Steel
- Imperial
- Dragonscale
- Dragonbone
- Falmer

Use as you wish, just remember to credit me for the work. 

Note: Please send me asg if you make this into a replacer for vanilla skeletons.
author: ScrooMoose
